==English==
===Alternative spellings===
In some usages (particularly old documents), words in the phrase may be capitalized, for example '''[[Party of the First Part]]'''.
===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[party]] [[of]] [[the]] [[first]] [[part]]|parties of the first part}}
#{{law}}{{archaic}}: the [[party]] to a [[legal]] [[dispute]] who first raised a [[complaint]] in a [[court]]
#{{law}}{{archaic}}: the first party named in a [[contract]], generally the party agreeing to perform a duty thereunder